import React from "react";
import {
  OverlayContainer,
  OverlayCloseIcon,
  OverlayContent,
  OverlayHeaders,
  OverlayNumber,
  OverlayName,
  OverlayTypes,
  OverlayType,
  OverlayImg,
  OverlayFooter,
  OverlayAddButton,
  OverlayStats,
  OverlayStat,
} from "./PokemonOverlayElements";
import closeIcon from "../../assets/images/closeIcon.png";
const PokemonOverlay = () => {
  return (
    <OverlayContainer>
      <OverlayCloseIcon src={closeIcon} />
      <OverlayContent>
        <OverlayHeaders>
          <OverlayNumber>
            #798 <OverlayName>Xurtree</OverlayName>
          </OverlayNumber>
          <OverlayTypes>
            <OverlayType>Electric</OverlayType>
          </OverlayTypes>
          <OverlayImg />
          <OverlayFooter>
            <OverlayAddButton></OverlayAddButton>
            <OverlayStats>
              <OverlayStat>HP: 73</OverlayStat>
              <OverlayStat>SP. Attack: 190</OverlayStat>
              <OverlayStat>Defense: 73</OverlayStat>
              <OverlayStat>Speed: 73</OverlayStat>
              <OverlayStat>Attack: 79</OverlayStat>
            </OverlayStats>
          </OverlayFooter>
        </OverlayHeaders>
      </OverlayContent>
    </OverlayContainer>
  );
};

export default PokemonOverlay;
